Title: d=2, N=2 Superconformal Symmetries and Models

Authors: Francois Delduc, Francois Gieres and Stephane Gourmelen

Comments: 43 pages, latex

Journal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 14 (1997) 1623-1649

We discuss the following aspects of two-dimensional N=2 supersymmetricand (2,2) superconformal structures in terms of Beltrami coefficients andformulation of superconformal models on such surfaces (invariant actions,anomalies and compensating actions, Ward identities).